sequenceDiagram
participant User
participant API
participant BusinessLogic
participant Database

User->>API: API Call (Review Submission)
API->>BusinessLogic: Validate and Process Request
BusinessLogic->>Database: Save Data
Database-->>BusinessLogic: Confirm Save (OK / Error)
BusinessLogic-->>API: Return Response (code 200/500)
API-->>User: HTTP Response (JSON + Code 201/400/403/409)
